			<p>
			<h1>Current Project Work in IIT Bombay</h1>
			<hr/>	
			<ol>
				<li><b>On Usability of TV UHF Band in India for Rural Broadband Access</b> <br/>
				<i>Guided by Prof Abhay Karandikar</i><br/>
				A testbed has been developed at Palghar, Maharashtra where our team has tested the working of WiFi (802.11g) in TV UHF band. Details regarding the testbed can be found <a href="https://www.ee.iitb.ac.in/tvws">here</a>.</b><br/>
				
				</li><br/><br/>
				<li><b>Collaboration with NICT, Japan to test the performance of LTE in TV UHF band</b><br/>
				<i>Guided by Prof Abhay karandikar </i><br/>
				Our team has collaborated with NICT, Japan to test the working of LTE in TV UHF band.
				</li><br/><br/>
