			<p>
			<h1>Projects during B.Tech </h1>
			<hr/>
			<ol>		 
				<li><b>Fingerprint Verification System</b> (B.Tech final year project)<br/>
				<i>Guided by Prof J. N. Sarvaiya</i> <br/>
				Researched about various algorithms used in various steps of fingerprint verification like gabor filtering etc. Finally, developed a matlab code to implement a complete fingerprint verification algorithm. </li> <br/><br/>
				<li><b>Text to Speech Conversion</b>(Summer Internship project in IIT, Delhi)<br/>
				<i>Guided by Prof Brijesh Lal </i><br/>
				A TTS library (flite) was build on the processor TMS320C5510. It involved installing dsp/bios kernel on the DSP processor and then porting the library onto it. The project involved detailed study of TMS320C55x processors and the how a text to speech library is built. </li><br/><br/>

				<li><b>Swarm Robotics</b><br/> 
				Built a pair of robots which communicated wirelessly. Also, these robots could traverse grid and were used to implement a specific set of instruction that were the part of the game.</li><br/>
			</ol>
			</p>


